# Tiny Python Project

This is a follow-along repository of Tiny Python Project's Book.

## How to run

- setup virtualenv: `pyenv virtualenv 3.12 tiny-python-projects`
- activate virtualenv: `pyenv local tiny-python-projects`
- making sure it is active: `pyenv which python`, `pyenv which pip`
- manually activate and deactivate: `pyenv activate tiny-python-projects`, `pyenv deactivate tiny-python-projects`

## References

- [More about pyenv](https://realpython.com/intro-to-pyenv/)